title: Season of Stephen King?! American Horror Story : Double Feature - Episode 1 Review and Reaction!
author: Molly Bee
comment: Reminds me of the beginning of Desperation.
description:
#AmericanHorrorStory #AHS #DoubleFeature 

It's time for another season of American Horror Story! A lot of our favorites are returning this time around (including Sarah Paulson, Lily Rabe, Francis Conroy, and Evan Peters) - and I'm seeing a LOT of references that really make me think of Stephen King stories and settings (particularly The Shining and perhaps a little Salem's Lot). So far, I'm very excited for this season. What do you all think?
